🧀6 CHEESE Chicken Cordon Bleu pizza that will blow your minds away!🧀 We dressed up @shihlinsnacks XXL crispy chicken cutlet to create our very own meal at home❤️⁣⁣
⁣⁣
So the chicken formed the “crust” and slowly we topped it with 5 different kinds of cheese (Peppery Jack, Colby Jack, Raclette, grilling cheese, Mozarella, Cheddar) and finally ham! The second pic shows the chicken pizza with @shihlinsnacks sweet plum potato fries and seafood tempura⁣⁣
⁣⁣
Come join me in some fun by creating a unique dish using @shihlinsnacks snacks! Winner gets to walk away with a year’s worth of crispy chicken 😝😝 @dressacake @baking_taitai @chrissy2090⁣⁣
⁣⁣
To Participate, simply⁣⁣
1) Create an awe inspiring meal using treats from @shihlinsnacks ⁣⁣
2)Snap an aesthetic photo oh your Zhng up creation ⁣⁣
3)Upload your photo with hashtag #ZhngItUpwithShihlin and tag 3 friends to enter⁣⁣
4) All participants must ‘Like’ Facebook page (fb.com/shihlinsnacks) or ‘Follow’ @shihlinsnacks on Instagram⁣⁣
